Sample API Documentation
Consent Update API
Endpoint

POST /api/v1/consent/update

Description

Updates customer consent preferences.

Request Headers
Header	Description
Authorization	OAuth Bearer Token
Content-Type	application/json
Correlation-Id	Request trace ID
Sample Request
{
  "customerId": "12345",
  "emailConsent": true,
  "smsConsent": false,
  "region": "EU",
  "consentTimestamp": "2026-05-26T10:00:00Z"
}
Sample Response

  "status": "SUCCESS",
  "message": "Consent Updated Successfully"
}
Error Codes
Code	Meaning
400	Invalid payload
401	Unauthorized
403	Consent validation failed
500	Internal server error
